span class=\"card-hr\">HR 0.76</span></div><div class=\"card\"><span class=\"card-label\">Lancet 2026</span><span class=\"card-body\">膵外作用の包括的レビュー</span><span class=\"card-hr\">総説</span></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
