    "num": 5,
    "title": "臨床での実践アクション",
    "style": "light",
    "content": "GLP-1RA処方のポイント、副腎偶発腫の3検査、AI診断の伝え方",
    "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#134e4a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);color:#0d9488;font-size:15px;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px}.logo{font-size:15px;color:rgba(19,78,74,0.5)}.main{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:16px}.section-title{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:30px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:18px;margin-bottom:20px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;background:#14b8a6;width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#134e4a}.list-bold{font-weight:700}.footer{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(19,78,74,0.3)}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 05 / 08</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><div class=\"section-label\">結 ── 明日からの実践</div><div class=\"section-title\">学会知見を臨床に活かす</div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"list-bold\">GLP-1RA処方時</span>：「血糖を下げる」+「心臓・腎臓を守る」を患者に伝える</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"list-bold\">副腎偶発腫</span>：DST 1mg / メタネフリン / ARRの3検査を必ず実施</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"list-bold\">MACS</span>：サイズが小さくてもホルモン評価は省略しない</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"list-bold\">AI診断</span>：「支援ツール」として説明。最終判断は臨床医が行う</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">5</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"list-bold\">オンデマンド</span>：教育講演は7/31まで視聴可。事前登録を確認</span></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
